### Role Management Endpoints
### These endpoints allow administrators to manage user roles, specifically granting and revoking STAFF permissions

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@userId = 1

### 1. Grant STAFF role to a user
### POST /api/admin/users/{userId}/roles/staff
### Requires ADMIN role
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/{{userId}}/roles/staff
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Revoke STAFF role from a user
### DELETE /api/admin/users/{userId}/roles/staff
### Requires ADMIN role
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/{{userId}}/roles/staff
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 3. Get all users with STAFF role
### GET /api/admin/users/staff
### Requires ADMIN role
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/staff
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 4. Get all roles for a specific user
### GET /api/admin/users/{userId}/roles
### Requires ADMIN role
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/{{userId}}/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

