### Notes:
# - All endpoints require ADMIN role authentication
# - The STAFF role allows users to scan QR codes and verify check-in requests
# - Users can have multiple roles (USER, ADMIN, STAFF)
# - The USER role is automatically granted to all users
# - The ADMIN role is managed through the is_admin flag in user_profile table (legacy)
# - The STAFF role is managed through the new role system
